"excerpt_area": {"text": "前几天晚上，45 岁演员韩栋在直播间里透露自己现在不仅「没戏拍」，还「被房贷所困」。随后又摘下眼镜擦拭眼角，声音哽咽地哭诉：「拍戏吧没戏拍，直播吧没流量」，引发热议。舆论发酵后，不少网友对于他的说法表示不解，并质疑他怎么可能没戏拍，对他喊话不要哭穷。随后，他本人现身回应称，是跟直播间观众「开玩笑的互动」，让大家别真信... 详情>>>45 岁演员韩栋直播时哭诉无戏可拍，每月房贷都还不上，压力很大，本人回应：假的，开玩笑的"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-50b8d1aa4bc5ee722d9569640caf7e16.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2046060626775118765"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI8PXUkdbBoLMBEAMaCTExOTgxNzE3OSDTkIfRBjAAOL4BQBpyEzIwNDYwNjA2MjY3NzUxMTg3NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1780957631.958806", "card_id": "Q_27678021", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "口才好是一种怎样的体验？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我是个凡事不爱开口的人，一般言语上都是 让和顺从，但心里不是，是口是心非吗？可我分明觉得是因为我口才太烂啊…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a6793804860fa0468228e9ffca3430de_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/27678021"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I8PXUkdbBoLMBEAMaBzMyNTQxMTcgrsz0pQUwADiSAkAbcggyNzY3ODAyMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1780957631.959082", "card_id": "Q_2046846004071346926", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "司机高速倒车称孩子病了心急，交通法规与人情如何平衡？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2026 年 5 月 15 日，沪蓉高速湖北应城段。交警开展视频巡查时，发现一辆小车驶过出口后，直接减速进入应急车道，随后一路向后倒车，倒至出口后向右拐进匝道驶离。 交警立即锁定该车，并联系驾驶人陈某前来接受处理。陈某称自己未留意道路标志导致错过出口，由于孩子生病急于回家，便心存侥幸倒车回到出口以节省时间。 交警对其进行了严肃的批评和安全教育，提醒他上有老下有小更应时刻将安全放在第一位，并依法对其在高速上倒车的违法行为予以处罚，同时驾驶证记 12 分。 交 警 提 醒 高速上错过路口，唯一、正确的做法是「将错就错」继续向前行驶，到前方出口下高速后再重新规划路线！绝对不允许急刹减速、强行变道、停车、倒车或逆行！ 错过高速路口直接倒车，司机：「孩子病了，我心急」"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2046846004071346926"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI8PXUkdbBoLMBEAMaCTExOTg0ODcwMSDDx5LRBjAAODJAHHITMjA0Njg0NjAwNDA3MTM0NjkyNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1780957631.959789", "card_id": "Q_1945988622634423934", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "朋友，可以推荐一些你觉得很值得一看的电影吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "电影推荐"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-270f98df4b1bb1c2f07e82cdec8196ff_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1945988622634423934"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI8PXUkdbBoLMBEAMaCTExNjQzNDkzMiCC8tbFBjAAOE5AHXITMTk0NTk4ODYyMjYzNDQyMzkzNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}]}